{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6f9c89cd78bcb394b3030ee213b\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-05-18 11:50 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yousan(叶枝君) (ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"name\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"bb360cd9","parentId":"69b1d6c0","timestamp":"2026-05-18T03:50:13.488Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"ac0627eb","parentId":"bb360cd9","timestamp":"2026-05-18T03:50:30.875Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about how to handle the case where the person who @mentions me (荒井花) should be set as the creator/requester of the bug/story ticket. This is about TAPD story/bug creation where the \"创建人\" (creator) should be set to whoever @mentioned me in the chat.\n\nThe question is: when someone @s me to create a requirement/bug, how should the creator field be handled?\n\nThis is a design question about the workflow. Let me think about this:\n\n1. TAPD bug/story creator is typically the logged-in user (叶枝君's cookies are used, so creator would always be 叶枝君)\n\n\n2. The challenge is that since we're using 叶枝君's TAPD credentials, the system will always record them as the creator. I could try setting the \"发起人\" or \"创建人\" field directly if TAPD's API allows it, or mention the actual requester's name in the ticket description or title. The most practical approach given the authentication constraint is to acknowledge that the creator will show as 叶枝君 in TAPD, but I can capture who actually requested it through other fields.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"这是个好问题。由于提单用的是叶枝君的 TAPD Cookie，**创建人字段会永远显示叶枝君**，TAPD 没有办法直接改创建人（那是系统字段）。\n\n有几个方案：\n\n**方案 A：在描述里注明（最简单）**  \n自动在描述开头加一行：`> 由 [xxx] 提报`，明确知道是谁提的\n\n**方案 B：设置\"发现人\"字段**  \nTAPD bug 单有\"发现人\"字段，可以把 @你的人设成发现人，语义上也合理\n\n**方案 C：让 @你的人自己登录提单**  \n需要收集每个同事的 TAPD Cookie，维护成本高，不太现实\n\n**方案 D：A + B 组合**  \n描述里写提报人，发现人也设成对方，双保险\n\n---\n\n你倾向哪种？我觉得 **B（发现人）+ A（描述备注）** 最合适，既清晰又不需要额外维护。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779076213488,"responseId":"chatcmpl-63bc35a2-6229-4658-badd-7d6b81187af4"}}
