{"type":"message","id":"e9749775","parentId":"d3a74d64","timestamp":"2026-05-18T03:53:59.000Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user says the CC (抄送人) on the bug ticket is incorrect. Let me check the bug ticket and fix it. The bug was created at https://www.tapd.cn/tapd_fe/31253609/bug/detail/1131253609001016529\n\nAccording to SKILL.md, default CC for code bugs is 周以天 (兵王). But the user says it's incorrect. They might want no CC, or a different person.\n\nLet me ask what the correct CC should be, or check if maybe the CC field format was wrong and ended up setting something unexpected.\n\nActually, looking at the debug output: \"Handler hidden value: 叶枝君;\" and \"Handler display value: 叶枝君(叶枝君);\" - and CC was set to 周以天. \n\n\nSince the user only asked to assign the bug to 叶枝君 without specifying a CC, I should ask them what the correct CC should be or offer to remove it entirely.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"抱歉！请问正确的抄送人应该是谁？我去改一下 bug 单。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779076428818,"responseId":"chatcmpl-aaecbb2c-8a73-4ddb-ab5c-f8131ad86c2c"}}
