{"type":"message","id":"8247fa05","parentId":"46cad74f","timestamp":"2026-05-18T03:54:52.012Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying the CC person should be 周以天, but the actual bug was created under 叶枝君's account, so the CC shows as 叶枝君 (the creator). Let me understand - the CC field didn't work correctly. The user is saying the CC person shown is 叶枝君 instead of 周以天.\n\nLet me check what happened - in the debug script, CC wasn't actually set. Looking at the debug script, I didn't include CC setting. Let me check the create_bug.mjs - it does have CC logic but uses `#BugCcValue` which may not exist.\n\nThe user wants me to fix the CC on the existing bug (1131253609001016529) to be 周以天, and also fix the create_bug.mjs script going forward.\n\n\nNow I'll write a script to update the CC field on that existing bug.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了，CC 没填上周以天。我去编辑那个 bug 单修正一下，顺便也修 create_bug.mjs 里的 CC 逻辑。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_016TmyrErLizZFuHBXT5vwwB","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\fix_bug_cc.mjs","content":"/**\n * 修复 Bug 单抄送人\n */\nimport { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));\nconst WS_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst COOKIES_FILE = path.join(WS_DIR, 'tapd_cookies.json');\n\nconst BUG_ID = '1131253609001016529';\nconst WORKSPACE_ID = '31253609';\nconst EDIT_URL = `https://www.tapd.cn/${WORKSPACE_ID}/bugtrace/bugs/edit?id=${BUG_ID}`;\n\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, 'utf8'));\nconst STEALTH = `Object.defineProperty(navigator,'webdriver',{get:()=>undefined});window.chrome={runtime:{}};`;\n\nconst browser = await chromium.launch({ headless: false, args: ['--no-sandbox'] });\nconst ctx = await browser.newContext({\n  userAgent: 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/120.0.0.0 Safari/537.36',\n  viewport: { width: 1280, height: 900 },\n});\nawait ctx.addInitScript(STEALTH);\nawait ctx.addCookies(cookies);\nconst page = await ctx.newPage();\n\nconsole.log('Opening bug edit page...');\nawait page.goto(EDIT_URL, { waitUntil: 'networkidle', timeout: 30000 });\n\n// 找 CC 输入框并填写周以天\nconsole.log('Setting CC to 周以天...');\nconst ccInput = page.locator('#BugCcValue');\nif (await ccInput.count() > 0) {\n  await ccInput.click();\n  await page.waitForTimeout(300);\n  await ccInput.fill('');\n  await ccInput.type('周以天', { delay: 150 });\n  await page.waitForTimeout(2500);\n  await page.keyboard.press('Enter');\n  await page.waitForTimeout(500);\n  console.log('CC set via autocomplete');\n} else {\n  console.warn('CC input not found');\n}\n\n// 检查CC值\nconst ccHidden = await page.locator('#BugCc').inputValue().catch(() => 'N/A');\nconsole.log('CC hidden value:', ccHidden);\n\n// 提交\nawait page.locator('a#_view, a.for_submit').first().click();\nawait page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n\nconst finalUrl = page.url();\nconsole.log('Final URL:', finalUrl);\n\nawait browser.close();\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779076472689,"responseId":"chatcmpl-e809a9ab-ebbe-4e55-9ebc-e97c52bb4ef4"}}
