{"type":"message","id":"86b136ea","parentId":"833afdd8","timestamp":"2026-05-18T03:58:25.550Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_0168VqUfzCVVgWAWxTzpQuPR","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Opening bug edit page...\nSetting CC via autocomplete...\nCC hidden value after autocomplete: 周以天;\nSubmitting bug_form via JS...\nSubmit result: submitted\nFinal URL: https://www.tapd.cn/tapd_fe/31253609/bug/list?confId=1131253609001007275"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":16696,"aggregated":"Opening bug edit page...\nSetting CC via autocomplete...\nCC hidden value after autocomplete: 周以天;\nSubmitting bug_form via JS...\nSubmit result: submitted\nFinal URL: https://www.tapd.cn/tapd_fe/31253609/bug/list?confId=1131253609001007275","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779076705550}}
{"type":"message","id":"316cb925","parentId":"86b136ea","timestamp":"2026-05-18T03:58:32.254Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ 成功了！跳转到 bug 列表页，说明编辑已保存。\n\n抄送人周以天已修正。总结一下问题所在：\n- **编辑页**的提交需要直接调 `form.submit()`，不是点按钮\n- **创建页**用 `a#_view` 点击才对\n\n我会把这个差异更新到 `create_bug.mjs` 里，后续编辑 bug 单时用正确的方式。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779076705551,"responseId":"chatcmpl-0224d4ae-abd6-4256-a075-f880334d596b"}}
