{"type":"message","id":"4bbd8dac","parentId":"686a0332","timestamp":"2026-05-18T03:59:58.844Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to open different sessions for different tasks. This is about session management in OpenClaw.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白主人！不同任务开不同 session，这样上下文不互相污染，也方便并行处理。\n\nOpenClaw 目前的 session 机制：\n- **主 session**（当前这个）：日常对话、快速任务\n- **sub-agent**：通过 `sessions_spawn` 开的后台任务 session，完成后自动汇报\n\n如果你说的是**手动开不同的对话窗口**来处理不同任务（比如一个专门跑热更、一个专门提单），这个需要在飞书/客户端侧操作——直接开多个对话或者用不同的 bot 账号。\n\n**我这边能做的：**\n1. 长任务（热更流水线、Playwright 提单）→ 自动 `sessions_spawn` 到子 session，主 session 保持响应\n2. 需要隔离上下文的任务 → 子 session 用 `context: isolated`，互不干扰\n\n你希望的是哪种场景？是想让我自动按任务类型分流，还是有其他具体需求？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779076786264,"responseId":"chatcmpl-bcdbc4ac-588f-4eda-9b57-456b229be49c"}}
