{"type":"message","id":"167e5968","parentId":"b6fdef79","timestamp":"2026-05-18T04:01:27.947Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants automatic task routing to different sessions. Let me think about how to implement this and document it.\n\nThe idea is: when a task comes in, automatically determine if it should run in a sub-agent session vs the main session, and spawn accordingly.\n\nLet me define the routing rules and document them in TOOLS.md or AGENTS.md.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！我来定义一套自动分流规则，记录到 TOOLS.md 里。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_01NReD35JvsyJEFP7HFaDasU","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\TOOLS.md","edits":[{"oldText":"## Skills (My Custom Workflows)","newText":"## Session 自动分流规则\n\n收到任务时，按以下规则决定是在主 session 处理还是开子 session：\n\n| 任务类型 | 处理方式 | 说明 |\n|---------|---------|------|\n| 日常对话、快速查询 | 主 session | 秒级完成，无需分流 |\n| **更新测试服**（热更流水线）| `sessions_spawn` 子 session | Unity 构建耗时长，主 session 保持响应 |\n| **提 Bug / 需求单**（TAPD）| `sessions_spawn` 子 session | Playwright 跑浏览器，耗时 30s+ |\n| 文件读写、代码修改 | 主 session | 快速操作 |\n| 需要等待的长任务（>10s）| `sessions_spawn` 子 session | 通用规则 |\n\n**分流原则：**\n- 预计 >10 秒的任务 → 子 session（`context: isolated`）\n- 子 session 完成后主动通知主人结果\n- 主 session 收到任务后立即回复「已开始/正在处理」，不让主人干等\n\n## Skills (My Custom Workflows)"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779076874846,"responseId":"chatcmpl-3ddba5f4-87c7-44ec-aff0-1dd6958e974f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d3a07420","parentId":"167e5968","timestamp":"2026-05-18T04:01:28.037Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01NReD35JvsyJEFP7HFaDasU","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\TOOLS.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n  38 ---\n  39 \n  40 Add whatever helps you do your job. This is your cheat sheet.\n  41 \n+ 42 ## Session 自动分流规则\n+ 43 \n+ 44 收到任务时，按以下规则决定是在主 session 处理还是开子 session：\n+ 45 \n+ 46 | 任务类型 | 处理方式 | 说明 |\n+ 47 |---------|---------|------|\n+ 48 | 日常对话、快速查询 | 主 session | 秒级完成，无需分流 |\n+ 49 | **更新测试服**（热更流水线）| `sessions_spawn` 子 session | Unity 构建耗时长，主 session 保持响应 |\n+ 50 | **提 Bug / 需求单**（TAPD）| `sessions_spawn` 子 session | Playwright 跑浏览器，耗时 30s+ |\n+ 51 | 文件读写、代码修改 | 主 session | 快速操作 |\n+ 52 | 需要等待的长任务（>10s）| `sessions_spawn` 子 session | 通用规则 |\n+ 53 \n+ 54 **分流原则：**\n+ 55 - 预计 >10 秒的任务 → 子 session（`context: isolated`）\n+ 56 - 子 session 完成后主动通知主人结果\n+ 57 - 主 session 收到任务后立即回复「已开始/正在处理」，不让主人干等\n+ 58 \n  42 ## Skills (My Custom Workflows)\n  43 \n  44 **群聊规范:** 每次在群里收到 @消息时，先立即回复一句礼貌性回应（如\"收到\"\"好的\"\"来了\"等），再开始处理需求。不要让群里的人等着没反应。\n  45 \n     ...","firstChangedLine":42},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779076888037}}
{"type":"message","id":"0a07b0cd","parentId":"d3a07420","timestamp":"2026-05-18T04:01:35.415Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"规则已记录！总结一下分流逻辑：\n\n- **秒级任务**（查询、改文件、聊天）→ 主 session 直接处理\n- **耗时任务**（更新测试服、提 TAPD 单、Playwright 自动化）→ 自动 `sessions_spawn` 子 session，我立即回「已开始」，完成后再通知你结果\n- **主 session 始终保持响应**，不会因为后台任务卡住\n\n下次你说「更新测试服」或「提个单」，我就自动后台跑，不让你等 🌸"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779076888038,"responseId":"chatcmpl-78649793-40eb-428e-ab66-6e8c50df3c91"}}
