{"type":"message","id":"622da6b3","parentId":"696c0687","timestamp":"2026-05-18T09:33:39.192Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is pointing out that the @mention format I used was wrong. Looking at the message, it seems the format sent was `<at user_id=ou_348eeddd81d4c03865f9f1684fce6966>` without quotes around the user_id value. The correct format should be `<at user_id=\"ou_348eeddd81d4c03865f9f1684fce6966\">`.\n\nLet me check TOOLS.md and MEMORY.md for the correct format, which I know from context is:\n`<at user_id=\"ou_348eeddd81d4c03865f9f1684fce6966\">兵王(周以天)</at>`\n\n\nI need to update the instructions for future sub-agents to ensure they use properly quoted attributes in the @mention format.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了，是引号问题！正确格式是：\n\n```\n<at user_id=\"ou_348eeddd81d4c03865f9f1684fce6966\">兵王(周以天)</at>\n```\n\n`user_id` 的值必须用英文双引号包裹，缺了引号飞书不会解析成真实 @ 提醒。\n\n我去把热更任务的 prompt 里的格式修正，同时更新 TOOLS.md 备注一下："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_01DsSs8b29rmCDEfWfaTZXjv","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\TOOLS.md","edits":[{"oldText":"真正的 @ 提及格式：`<at user_id=\"open_id\">显示名字</at>`","newText":"真正的 @ 提及格式：`<at user_id=\"open_id\">显示名字</at>`\n- ⚠️ `user_id` 属性值**必须用英文双引号包裹**，缺引号飞书不解析，变成普通文字"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779096807247,"responseId":"chatcmpl-dda23021-8eff-48e7-9eeb-5d2d1ab74277"}}
