{"type":"message","id":"4aeb8d17","parentId":"ba30c73f","timestamp":"2026-05-18T09:34:33.718Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01FUEbMaqJKPg2j5hpKufDr6","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"edit\",\n  \"error\": \"Could not find the exact text in C:\\\\Users\\\\yyzypublic\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\MEMORY.md. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\\nCurrent file contents:\\n# MEMORY.md\\n\\n## 热更流水线配置（2026-05-15）\\n\\n### 执行方式\\n- **入口：** `RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat`\\n- **Unity 路径：** `C:\\\\Program Files\\\\Unity\\\\Hub\\\\Editor\\\\2020.3.49f1\\\\Editor\\\\Unity.exe`\\n- **入口方法：** `YYZY.BuildPipeline.BuildPipeline.RunHotUpdatePipeline`\\n- **默认增量构建**（不清 Bundles 缓存，速度快。仅资源丢失或异常时才全量）\\n\\n### 更新测试服流程\\n1. 检查是否有 Unity 进程在执行 `RunHotUpdatePipeline`\\n2. 关掉所有 Unity Editor 进程\\n3. Git pull\\n4. 运行 RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat\\n5. 完成后在「月圆之夜CCG开发群」`oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77` @兵王 `ou_348eeddd81d4c03865f9f1684fce6966` 通知\\n\\n## TAPD 自动提单（进行中 - 2026-05-15）\\n\\n### 进度\\n- ✅ Playwright 已安装（v1.60.0）\\n- ✅ WAF 已绕过，成功加载 TAPD 登录页（`cloud_logins/login`）\\n- ✅ 微信扫码二维码已显示（`mp.weixin.qq.com`）\\n- ⏳ **待完成：** 扫码登录后走通提单流程\\n\\n### 登录方式选择\\n主人选了**微信扫码登录**，二维码页面已调通，扫一扫即可登录。\\n登录后保存 Cookie，后续分析提单页面结构（bug/需求表单字段）。\\n\\n## 同事白名单\\n\\n- **主人 Yousan(叶枝君)\\n... (truncated)\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"edit","error":"Could not find the exact text in C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\MEMORY.md. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\nCurrent file contents:\n# MEMORY.md\n\n## 热更流水线配置（2026-05-15）\n\n### 执行方式\n- **入口：** `RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat`\n- **Unity 路径：** `C:\\Program Files\\Unity\\Hub\\Editor\\2020.3.49f1\\Editor\\Unity.exe`\n- **入口方法：** `YYZY.BuildPipeline.BuildPipeline.RunHotUpdatePipeline`\n- **默认增量构建**（不清 Bundles 缓存，速度快。仅资源丢失或异常时才全量）\n\n### 更新测试服流程\n1. 检查是否有 Unity 进程在执行 `RunHotUpdatePipeline`\n2. 