{"type":"message","id":"b02264c4","parentId":"0394f63c","timestamp":"2026-05-18T10:06:40.081Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01H5pr9nt4VUw9E1VErRjQs7","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"﻿using System;\nusing UnityEngine;\nusing UnityEngine.UI;\n\nnamespace Gordian\n{\n    public class GordianEquipmentBagView : BaseView\n    {\n        /* -------- AUTO GENERATED COMPONENT FIELDS START -------- */\n\t\tprotected Button m_BgButton;\n\t\tprotected Text m_TitleText;\n\t\tprotected Button m_CloseButton;\n\t\tprotected RectTransform m_ContentTransform;\n\t\tprotected Button m_UnequipButton;\n\n\t\tpublic Action OnBgButtonCallback { get; set; }\n\t\tpublic Action OnCloseButtonCallback { get; set; }\n\t\tpublic Action OnUnequipButtonCallback { get; set; }\n\n\t\tprotected override void BindComponents(GameObject go)\n\t\t{\n\t\t\tvar autoBindTool = go.GetComponent<AutoBindTool>();\n\n\t\t\tm_BgButton = autoBindTool.BindComponent<Button>(0);\n\t\t\tm_TitleText = autoBindTool.BindComponent<Text>(1);\n\t\t\tm_CloseButton = autoBindTool.BindComponent<Button>(2);\n\t\t\tm_ContentTransform = autoBindTool.BindComponent<RectTransform>(3);\n\t\t\tm_UnequipButton = autoBindTool.BindComponent<Button>(4);\n\t\t}\n        /* -------- AUTO GENERATED COMPONENT FIELDS END -------- */\n\n        protected override void InitView()\n        {\n            base.InitView();\n        }\n\n        protected override void InitEvent()\n        {\n            m_BgButton.onClick.AddListener(OnCloseButton);\n            m_CloseButton.onClick.AddListener(OnCloseButton);\n            m_UnequipButton.onClick.AddListener(OnUnequipButton);\n        }\n\n        private void OnUnequipButton()\n        {\n            OnUnequipButtonCallback?.Invoke();\n        }\n\n        private void OnCloseButton()\n        {\n            GordianUIManager.Instance.CloseForm(UIFormId.GordianEquipmentBagPanel);\n        }\n\n        protected override void RemoveEvent()\n        {\n            base.RemoveEvent();\n\n            m_BgButton.onClick.RemoveAllListeners();\n            m_CloseButton.onClick.RemoveAllListeners();\n        }\n\n        public void ShowUnequip(bool value)\n        {\n            m_UnequipButton.SetActive(value);\n        }\n\n        public override void Close()\n        {\n            base.Close();\n        }\n\n        public virtual void AddCard(GordianCard card)\n        {\n            card.transform.SetParent(m_ContentTransform);\n            card.transform.Reset();\n\n            card.transform.localScale = Vector3.one * 0.7f;\n        }\n\n        public void SetTitle(string value)\n        {\n            m_TitleText.text = value;\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779098800081}}
{"type":"message","id":"3f72de14","parentId":"b02264c4","timestamp":"2026-05-18T10:06:50.483Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"代码层面看不出问题——装备卡是直接 `SetParent(m_ContentTransform)` 塞进去的，滚动应该由 ScrollView 自动处理。但 3 排放不下时不能滚，**多半是 Prefab 里的 ScrollView/Content 配置问题**：\n\n1. **Content 没有 `ContentSizeFitter`** → 高度固定，卡牌超出后被裁剪，滚不了\n2. **VerticalLayoutGroup 的 `Child Control Height` 没勾** → Content 高度不会随子节点数量撑开\n3. **Mask/Viewport 设置不对** → 滚动区域判断有问题\n\n这些需要在 Unity Editor 里改 Prefab。请问主人是手机端还是 PC 端的装备背包 Prefab 出问题？（`GordianEquipmentBagView` 还是 `GordianEquipmentBagPCView`？）"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779098800084,"responseId":"chatcmpl-1c155e5f-2aa7-40ce-a6ec-25ca435dc0f5"}}
