{"type":"message","id":"e1789c3a","parentId":"5b8dde07","timestamp":"2026-05-18T10:08:52.599Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"手机端也没有 ScrollRect。两个 Prefab 都没有，说明这个装备背包**本来就没设计滚动**，只是装备少时刚好够用，3 排时超出边界了。\n\n需要主人在 Unity Editor 里改 PC 端 Prefab，给装备列表容器加上 ScrollRect。具体操作：\n\n1. 打开 `ArtPackage_PC/Gordian/Prefab/GordianEquipmentBagPanel_PC.prefab`\n2. 找到装备卡片列表的父节点（即代码里绑定的 index=2 的节点 `m_ContentTransform`）\n3. 在它外面套一层 ScrollView（或者直接在它上加 ScrollRect + Mask），设置垂直滚动\n4. 给 Content（m_ContentTransform）加 `ContentSizeFitter`（垂直方向 = Preferred Size）和 `VerticalLayoutGroup`（或 GridLayoutGroup）\n\n需要我在代码侧做什么配合（比如初始化后强制刷新 layout）吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779098921409,"responseId":"chatcmpl-dbf6ad65-c8e4-49c3-98c3-5152b22f8763"}}
