{"type":"message","id":"98c0511c","parentId":"d9bd2b06","timestamp":"2026-05-18T10:46:52.456Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在更新 MEMORY.md："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_0117CiuMZKGS7JuBdQ1FZ5Ag","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\MEMORY.md","edits":[{"oldText":"## TAPD Playwright 提单经验（2026-05-18）\n\n- **创建页**提交：点 `a#_view`， headless 不可用，必须 **headed 模式**（`headless: false`）\n- **编辑页**提交：直接 JS `document.getElementById('bug_form').submit()`，不要点按钮\n- CC 字段：`#BugCcValue`（显示）+ `#BugCc`（隐藏，`data[Bug][cc]`），自动补全后按 Enter\n- 研发分支 `#BugCustomFieldOne` 是 **select** 类型，用 `selectOption` 而非 `fill`\n- 脚本路径：`workspace/scripts/create_bug.mjs`","newText":"## TAPD Playwright 提单经验（2026-05-18）\n\n- **创建页**提交：点 `a#_view`， headless 不可用，必须 **headed 模式**（`headless: false`）\n- **编辑页**提交：直接 JS `document.getElementById('bug_form').submit()`，不要点按钮\n- CC 字段：`#BugCcValue`（显示），用 `.first()` + `.type()` + `Enter`，等 2s 再按\n- 处理人：`#BugCurrentOwnerValue` 用 `.first().type()` + 等 2s + `Enter`，多人依次输入\n- 附件：`#file_input` 有多个元素，必须用 `.first().setInputFiles()`，等 4s 再进行下一步\n- 研发分支 `#BugCustomFieldOne` 是 **select** 类型，用 `selectOption` 而非 `fill`\n- 脚本路径：`workspace/scripts/create_bug.mjs`"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779101190131,"responseId":"chatcmpl-e91cc9f6-2201-4967-9bd4-f10f60219a76"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8822344b","parentId":"98c0511c","timestamp":"2026-05-18T10:46:52.468Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_0117CiuMZKGS7JuBdQ1FZ5Ag","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\MEMORY.md."}],"details":{"diff":"    ...\n 72 ## TAPD Playwright 提单经验（2026-05-18）\n 73 \n 74 - **创建页**提交：点 `a#_view`， headless 不可用，必须 **headed 模式**（`headless: false`）\n 75 - **编辑页**提交：直接 JS `document.getElementById('bug_form').submit()`，不要点按钮\n-76 - CC 字段：`#BugCcValue`（显示）+ `#BugCc`（隐藏，`data[Bug][cc]`），自动补全后按 Enter\n+76 - CC 字段：`#BugCcValue`（显示），用 `.first()` + `.type()` + `Enter`，等 2s 再按\n+77 - 处理人：`#BugCurrentOwnerValue` 用 `.first().type()` + 等 2s + `Enter`，多人依次输入\n+78 - 附件：`#file_input` 有多个元素，必须用 `.first().setInputFiles()`，等 4s 再进行下一步\n 77 - 研发分支 `#BugCustomFieldOne` 是 **select** 类型，用 `selectOption` 而非 `fill`\n 78 - 脚本路径：`workspace/scripts/create_bug.mjs`\n 79 \n 80 ## TAPD 自动提单 Skill\n    ...","firstChangedLine":76},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779101212468}}
{"type":"message","id":"61e69877","parentId":"8822344b","timestamp":"2026-05-18T10:46:59.152Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"同时更新 SKILL.md："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_01M2Q41LehQBBfGenHEJfCEd","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/tapd-bug-create/SKILL.md","offset":50,"limit":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779101212471,"responseId":"chatcmpl-6128cee5-b67a-41b0-af92-5943cf045369"}}
{"type":"message","id":"795e1544","parentId":"61e69877","timestamp":"2026-05-18T10:46:59.161Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01M2Q41LehQBBfGenHEJfCEd","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The `#save_return` input is `display: none` — do not click it directly.\n\n### Upload Attachments (Images)\n\nTAPD uses `#file_input` (`<input type=\"file\">`) for file upload.\nPlaywright's `setInputFiles()` works even on hidden inputs:\n\n```javascript\n// Upload images to the bug\nawait page.locator('#file_input').first().setInputFiles('path/to/screenshot.jpg');\nawait page.waitForTimeout(3000); // Wait for AJAX upload to complete\n\n// Upload multiple files sequentially\nfor (const filePath of attachmentPaths) {\n  await page.locator('#file_input').first().setInputFiles(filePath);\n  await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n}\n```\n\nWhen the user sends images/messages with player feedback screenshots:\n1. Save the attachments from `media/inbound/`\n2. Pass as `attachments: [filePath1, filePath2]` to the create bug script\n3. Required: always include user-provided screenshots as bug evidence\n\n## Default Assignment Rules\n\n| Bug 类型 | 处理人 | 抄送人 |\n|----------|--------|--------|\n| 程序 (Code) | `叶枝君;` | `周以天;` |\n| 策划 (Design) | `赵乾;` | `周以天;` |\n\n[108 more lines in file. Use offset=80 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779101219161}}
{"type":"message","id":"c9155d82","parentId":"795e1544","timestamp":"2026-05-18T10:47:14.229Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_01D1FNmqbLjrxKRuDDw17UP4","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/tapd-bug-create/SKILL.md","edits":[{"oldText":"```javascript\n// Upload images to the bug\nawait page.locator('#file_input').first().setInputFiles('path/to/screenshot.jpg');\nawait page.waitForTimeout(3000); // Wait for AJAX upload to complete\n\n// Upload multiple files sequentially\nfor (const filePath of attachmentPaths) {\n  await page.locator('#file_input').first().setInputFiles(filePath);\n  await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n}\n```","newText":"```javascript\n// ⚠️ #file_input 页面上有多个元素，必须用 .first() 避免严格模式报错\nawait page.locator('#file_input').first().setInputFiles('path/to/screenshot.jpg');\nawait page.waitForTimeout(4000); // 等 4s，AJAX 上传需要时间\n\n// 多文件依次上传\nfor (const filePath of attachmentPaths) {\n  await page.locator('#file_input').first().setInputFiles(filePath);\n  await page.waitForTimeout(4000);\n}\n```"},{"oldText":"## Set Handler/CC - Autocomplete (IMPORTANT)\n\nThe handler and CC fields use TAPD's user autocomplete. **Do NOT set hidden fields directly** (will show as ID).\n\nCorrect approach (type name + press Enter):\n```javascript\nawait page.type('#BugCurrentOwnerValue', '谭佳钦', {delay: 100});\nawait page.waitForTimeout(2000);\nawait page.keyboard.press('Enter');\n// This triggers TAPD's autocomplete and properly resolves the user\n```","newText":"## Set Handler/CC - Autocomplete (IMPORTANT)\n\nThe handler and CC fields use TAPD's user autocomplete. **Do NOT set hidden fields directly** (will show as ID).\n\nCorrect approach (use `.first()` + `.type()` + wait 2s + Enter):\n```javascript\n// 处理人 - 多人依次输入\nconst ownerInput = page.locator('#BugCurrentOwnerValue').first();\nfor (const name of ['叶枝君', '周以天']) {\n  await ownerInput.click();\n  await ownerInput.type(name, { delay: 120 });\n  await page.waitForTimeout(2000); // 等自动补全加载\n  await page.keyboard.press('Enter');\n  await page.waitForTimeout(600);\n}\n\n// 抄送 - 同样方式\nconst ccInput = page.locator('#BugCcValue').first();\nawait ccInput.click();\nawait ccInput.type('周以天', { delay: 120 });\nawait page.waitForTimeout(2000);\nawait page.keyboard.press('Enter');\n```\n\n**注意：** `#BugCurrentOwnerValue` 和 `#BugCcValue` 页面上可能有多个，必须用 `.first()`"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779101219164,"responseId":"chatcmpl-0f5c924a-3c9c-40d6-b6ff-c971589167bf"}}
