102 const ccInput = page.locator('#BugCcValue').first();\n+103 await ccInput.click();\n+104 await ccInput.type('周以天', { delay: 120 });\n  92 await page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n  93 await page.keyboard.press('Enter');\n- 94 // This triggers TAPD's autocomplete and properly resolves the user\n  95 ```\n  96 \n+109 **注意：** `#BugCurrentOwnerValue` 和 `#BugCcValue` 页面上可能有多个，必须用 `.first()`\n+110 \n  97 ## Create a Story (Requirement)\n  98 \n  99 ```javascript\n 100 import { createStory } from './scripts/create_story.mjs';\n     ...","firstChangedLine":58},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779101234237}}
