{"type":"message","id":"a794d8cf","parentId":"341ee671","timestamp":"2026-05-18T11:24:54.024Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到关键了！上传流程是：\n1. 先上传到 `bugtemp`（临时区），entity_id = `1415287364192424341`（这是**草稿 ID**，不是 bug ID）\n2. 提交 bug_form 时，TAPD 会把 bugtemp 里的附件关联到正式 bug\n\n问题是：**编辑已有 bug 时，entity_id 是草稿 ID，附件上传到了临时区，但 form.submit() 没把它们正确关联到 bug `1131253609001016534`**。\n\n编辑页的附件上传流程跟创建页不同。最可靠的方案是直接调 TAPD 附件 API，用 `fetch` 直接上传到 bug："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_01Todk75gJshYGq5dyXVEdFm","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\upload_bug_attachment5.mjs","content":"/**\n * 直接调 TAPD 附件 API 上传到已有 bug 单\n * 绕过编辑页，用 add_attachment_drag API 直接关联\n */\nimport { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));\nconst WS_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst COOKIES_FILE = path.join(WS_DIR, 'tapd_cookies.json');\n\nconst BUG_ID = '1131253609001016534';\nconst WORKSPACE_ID = '31253609';\nconst ATTACHMENT_PATH = 'C:\\\\Users\\\\yyzypublic\\\\.openclaw\\\\media\\\\inbound\\\\3413db8c-85b9-44d3-a090-d07cf86b2cc4.jpg';\n\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, 'utf8'));\n\n// 构造 cookie 字符串\nconst cookieStr = cookies.map(c => `${c.name}=${c.value}`).join('; ');\n\n// 读取文件\nconst fileBuffer = fs.readFileSync(ATTACHMENT_PATH);\nconst filename = path.basename(ATTACHMENT_PATH);\n\n// 用 FormData API 上传（Node.js 18+ 内置）\n// TAPD 附件直接上传 API：/31253609/attachments/add_attachment_drag/Bug/{bugId}/security\nconst uploadUrl = `https://www.tapd.cn/${WORKSPACE_ID}/attachments/add_attachment_drag/Bug/${BUG_ID}/security?filename=${encodeURIComponent(filename)}`;\n\nconsole.log('上传到:', uploadUrl);\n\nconst formData = new FormData();\nconst blob = new Blob([fileBuffer], { type: 'image/jpeg' });\nformData.append('Filedata', blob, filename);\n\nconst response = await fetch(uploadUrl, {\n  method: 'POST',\n  headers: {\n    'Cookie': cookieStr,\n    'Referer': `https://www.tapd.cn/${WORKSPACE_ID}/bugtrace/bugs/view?id=${BUG_ID}`,\n    'Origin': 'https://www.tapd.cn',\n    'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/120.0.0.0 Safari/537.36',\n  },\n  body: formData,\n});\n\nconst responseText = await response.text();\nconsole.log('响应状态:', response.status);\nconsole.log('响应内容:', responseText.substring(0, 500));\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779103476326,"responseId":"chatcmpl-57f98c09-0366-4878-a0b6-fe352e3b8c73"}}
