{"type":"message","id":"6d35c4ec","parentId":"97db1bc9","timestamp":"2026-05-18T11:28:15.368Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"上传响应是空，说明文件没有正确传上去，点 `a#_view` 也没提交成功。\n\n这个问题比较复杂，TAPD 附件上传走的是异步 AJAX + 文件服务器，Playwright 的 `setInputFiles` 触发方式跟真实浏览器行为有差异。\n\n主人，建议**手动在 bug 单编辑页传一下截图**，手动操作最省事。后续如果要自动化附件，我再研究正确的 AJAX 触发方式。需要的话提供 bug 单链接：\n\nhttps://www.tapd.cn/tapd_fe/31253609/bug/detail/1131253609001016534"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779103686194,"responseId":"chatcmpl-2e0182bb-51b7-4139-9e2a-a22b0bb20645"}}
